*
!.gitignore
!composer/
!composer/**
!tasks/
!tasks/**
!glossaries/
!glossaries/**
!icon/
!icon/**
!readme/
!readme/**
# macOS signing entitlements (non-secret build input; committed)
!macos/
!macos/entitlements.plist
# Packaging sources used by scripts/build-all.sh (committed; not build output)
!linux-install.sh
!windows-installer.nsi
# Private build configuration: the sample is committed; build.properties (real
# secrets) stays ignored by the * rule above and must NEVER be committed.
!build.sample.properties
